class.name: gd_Interface_Statics
class.brief_description: Godot GDExtension bindings for Open CASCADE Interface_Statics static handle macros.
class.description:
This class provides documentation for the Interface_Statics static handle macros from Open CASCADE. No callable methods or properties are exposed in this binding, as the original header only defines macros for static handle management. See the original Interface_Statics.hxx for usage and initialization details.
Note: If future versions of Interface_Statics.hxx introduce Standard_EXPORT classes with callable methods, this documentation will be updated accordingly.
